    /*.•°:°.´+˚.*°.˚:*.´•*.+°.•°:´*.´•*.•°.•°:°.´:•˚°.*°.˚:*.´+°.•*/

    // If the ETH transfer MUST succeed with a reasonable gas budget, use the force variants.
    //
    // The regular variants:
